WEBVTT

00:00:32.479 --> 00:00:32.960
Bro Mao

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:35.960
Datou, stay behind.

00:00:36.119 --> 00:00:36.920
Everyone else can go.

00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:51.560
Bro Mao

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.359
Are we still in the real estate business?

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:56.479
What you shouldn't ask,

00:00:57.479 --> 00:00:58.280
don't ask.

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:12.280
What's yours,

00:01:14.159 --> 00:01:15.000
you'll get every penny.

00:01:24.519 --> 00:01:25.280
Thanks, Bro Mao.

00:01:25.599 --> 00:01:26.439
Get back to work.

00:01:28.879 --> 00:01:29.799
Just name a price.

00:01:37.359 --> 00:01:38.879
If I'm not mistaken,

00:01:39.719 --> 00:01:41.519
your big brother gave you this ring, right?

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.560
What's that supposed to mean?

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:46.280
Young man,

00:01:46.599 --> 00:01:48.079
you haven't found a worthy master.

00:01:48.879 --> 00:01:49.719
This thing

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:50.920
is just iron.

00:01:54.319 --> 00:01:55.680
Do you know what my big brother does?

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:57.760
I don't care what your brother does.

00:01:58.079 --> 00:01:59.280
If you don't believe me,

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:01.359
go out, turn left.

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:02.760
There's a scrapyard.

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:13.240
Boss Datou,

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:15.639
it's not just the cops after Bro Mao now.

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:18.240
Even the debts the boys lent out,

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.199
we can't collect them.

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.120
Those miserable bastards,

00:02:21.199 --> 00:02:22.439
once they heard Bro Mao got into trouble,

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.960
they can't wait for the company to collapse.

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:27.680
Small amounts are fine,

00:02:28.039 --> 00:02:29.039
but we can't get the big money back.

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:31.120
How are the boys gonna live, Boss Datou?

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:34.520
And now even the foot massage parlors

00:02:34.639 --> 00:02:36.599
and bars the boys run,

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.639
if this keeps up,

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:40.599
they're all gonna shut down.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:44.560
Boss Datou,

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:46.159
what do we do?

00:03:03.879 --> 00:03:05.039
Bro Mao's legacy,

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.319
I, Datou, will carry it on.

00:03:06.479 --> 00:03:07.039
Let's go.

00:03:24.159 --> 00:03:25.919
You want to take over?

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.439
Your name is Chen Yongjiang?

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:32.960
Where's Chen Yongjiang?

00:03:33.759 --> 00:03:35.520
On the arrest warrant.

00:03:37.719 --> 00:03:38.759
Let me tell you,

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:41.879
even if Chen Yongjiang showed up,

00:03:43.800 --> 00:03:45.319
it'd be useless.

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:46.639
You get it?

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:52.840
I... I'm Little Luo.

00:03:53.159 --> 00:03:55.000
I'm asking for a friend.

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:58.159
You said you wanted to open a branch.

00:03:58.199 --> 00:03:59.280
So it's...

00:04:00.479 --> 00:04:01.319
already done, huh?

00:04:01.479 --> 00:04:02.360
Then... never mind.

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:03.560
I'll let him know later.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.080
Let's catch up sometime.

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.120
Thanks, thanks.

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:08.400
Hey, Lao Yang.

00:04:08.639 --> 00:04:11.280
I'm looking to pick up some small businesses.

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:14.400
They're all closed, huh?

00:04:16.199 --> 00:04:17.720
If something suitable comes up, let me know.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.600
Okay, okay, okay.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:22.279
Lao Wang.

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:23.240
It's me.

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:25.519
Luo, yeah, yeah.

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.040
I've got a friend

00:04:27.399 --> 00:04:28.720
who wants to take over a shop.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:30.319
Do you...

00:04:30.399 --> 00:04:31.759
have any suitable shops?

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:33.879
Well...

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:34.759
all right then.

00:04:34.759 --> 00:04:36.839
Then... then I'll ask around later.

00:05:18.519 --> 00:05:19.319
I'm here to pick up my car.

00:05:21.279 --> 00:05:22.160
Sure, go ahead.

00:05:22.439 --> 00:05:24.240
But it's inconvenient to pay right now.

00:05:28.199 --> 00:05:30.279
Zhang Yuanshan, have I been too soft on you?

00:05:32.959 --> 00:05:34.399
Fine, don't pay me back.

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:36.439
The boys have nothing better to do anyway.

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:38.560
So I'll just wait you out.

00:05:39.319 --> 00:05:41.600
I'll wait until you shut down.

00:05:47.399 --> 00:05:48.120
Hello.

00:05:55.439 --> 00:05:56.360
You're Zhang Yuanshan, right?

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:00.959
I'm not too clear on Bro Mao's situation now.

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:03.199
But there's one thing I am sure of.

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.160
And that is...

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:06.399
you're definitely not getting away.

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:10.199
This auto repair shop...

00:06:10.399 --> 00:06:11.360
From what I know,

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:12.560
has three car lifts.

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:14.160
Each one's priced at 150,000.

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.439
That's 450,000 total.

00:06:15.879 --> 00:06:18.160
Plus the computer diagnostics,

00:06:18.199 --> 00:06:20.360
the paint booth, all that included,

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:21.319
you...

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:24.279
you reported 800,000 in total.

00:06:25.560 --> 00:06:27.319
So your actual job here

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:29.040
is handling money laundering for Bro Mao.

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:30.000
Right?

00:06:30.879 --> 00:06:32.480
Those receipts and bank records of yours...

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.000
once the cops check,

00:06:34.519 --> 00:06:35.959
all these bills and contracts

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:37.040
will be solid evidence.

00:06:37.759 --> 00:06:39.759
Bro Mao's money laundering accomplice.

00:06:40.079 --> 00:06:40.720
So,

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:42.319
you're definitely not getting away.

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:45.199
Hold on,

00:06:46.079 --> 00:06:46.879
are you

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:49.439
Bro Mao's guy or a cop?

00:06:50.920 --> 00:06:51.639
Me?

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.839
If I called the cops right now,

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:57.360
the boys might...

00:06:58.160 --> 00:06:59.240
they might all go in.

00:07:03.319 --> 00:07:04.079
But

00:07:04.639 --> 00:07:06.000
you'd never come out.

00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:07.600
Because in black and white,

00:07:07.639 --> 00:07:09.519
they're signed by you and Chen Yongjiang.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.560
If they go in,

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:12.959
they're just employees at most.

00:07:13.319 --> 00:07:14.279
But if you go in,

00:07:15.079 --> 00:07:16.040
you're the main culprit.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.720
Out here, I can't touch you.

00:07:22.079 --> 00:07:23.399
But inside? That's another story.

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:25.759
I've done time.

00:07:26.839 --> 00:07:28.079
I've got people inside.

00:07:30.519 --> 00:07:31.560
No, I...

00:07:32.399 --> 00:07:34.439
I really don't have any money.

00:07:35.439 --> 00:07:36.399
You can all see it.

00:07:36.759 --> 00:07:37.920
There's no business out there.

00:07:38.279 --> 00:07:39.759
Even if you take the shop,

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:40.879
you couldn't make it work either.

00:07:40.959 --> 00:07:41.759
That's perfect.

00:07:41.839 --> 00:07:42.600
Here's the thing.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:44.879
I've drafted a contract.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:48.920
I can, at market value,

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:51.759
buy ownership of Yuanshan Auto Repair.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.519
These boys don't have to move either.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:55.279
They can keep working here.

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:56.079
Of course,

00:07:56.079 --> 00:07:57.839
I can also pay off the debts you owe.

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.800
If you want a place to make a living,

00:07:59.879 --> 00:08:01.160
I can also consider

00:08:01.319 --> 00:08:02.439
letting you fix tires here.

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:04.240
Sound good?

00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:33.399
Oh, right.

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:35.840
I'll pay the repair shop's debt.

00:08:35.919 --> 00:08:36.840
This is the first installment.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:40.960
What are you trying to do?

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:43.639
Doing business. Acquiring shops.

00:08:43.799 --> 00:08:44.519
Making money.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.200
What were you doing at the cemetery?